snippet.title: Far Cry 4: Limited Edition Trailer
snippet.description:
Same as Fable Legends, not a huge fan of Far Cry but to the fans there, I'd figured get this trailer uploaded & be done with it. I'm looking to do a 5,000 views special soon so please continue to show your support by watching all my vids, comment nicely, sub to my channel & make it happen ok? Ok thanks.

Game: Far Cry 4: Limited Edition
Consoles: Xbox 360 & Xbox ONE
Available: All States 
Release Date: November 18th, 2014
Published By: Ubisoft
